              <p>Not only is it one of Japan’s oldest and most important cultural destinations, its proximity to so many other key attractions and cities within the greater Kansai Region (Mie, Nara, Wakayama, Kyoto, Osaka, Hyōgo and Shiga) makes it the ideal base for anybody looking to explore everything Japan has to offer from one amazing, central location.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- /s-entry-content -->

